{"tid":660431,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"【召集】有冇人做過全身麻醉嘅口腔手術？","createTime":"2018-05-10T16:15:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T02:41:07.000Z","uid":10464,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"bff5ce12db507c20942c04b2bfb5d7df6eefd595","tid":660431,"uid":10464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T16:15:53.000Z","msg":"就快入院做手術<br />\n係人生第一次手術<br />\n我因為智慧齒而生咗個囊腫（腫瘤）喺鼻竇嗰邊要拎咗佢<br />\n有啲不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望可以生勾勾出院<br />\n<br />\n想聽下大家分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n剝牙又好 乜都好 開心些牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全身麻醉好似幾恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：好廢 怕痛"},{"pid":"e0261d09c946ef872b3cce81cdb376a793ca75fe","tid":660431,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T16:16:43.000Z","msg":"麻醉咗 手術過程唔會痛嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd753a08b6be6522929e3a6c50791648e0caa2fa","tid":660431,"uid":63765,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T16:22:56.000Z","msg":"全新麻醉咗你就會瞓着咗無知覺又唔會痛 <br />\n無你想像中咁恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：試過做手術同全身麻醉<br />\n<br />\nBtw樓豬加油大膽啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe87e5c15ca4c8906ca28cb4fde488c53b904281","tid":660431,"uid":170725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bff5ce12db507c20942c04b2bfb5d7df6eefd595","tid":660431,"uid":10464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T16:15:53.000Z","msg":"就快入院做手術<br />\n係人生第一次手術<br />\n我因為智慧齒而生咗個囊腫（腫瘤）喺鼻竇嗰邊要拎咗佢<br />\n有啲不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望可以生勾勾出院<br />\n<br />\n想聽下大家分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n剝牙又好 乜都好 開心些牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全身麻醉好似幾恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：好廢 怕痛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T16:25:20.000Z","msg":"做過，同你一樣case 不過唔記得麻醉全身定剩係個口"},{"pid":"44f1b1f1a84903e23e1dbd786256ccaf91f7466f","tid":660431,"uid":10241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T16:28:24.000Z","msg":"同你一樣全身麻醉又係關智慧齒事<br />\n我覺得插鼻呼吸果個野痛過其他<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef62e6098dcc8923165ba8a7def51f9a368fa4d9","tid":660431,"uid":55936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T16:33:08.000Z","msg":"好似俾人迷暈咗，醒咗咩都唔知淨係覺得口腔有啲痛，keep住食止痛藥都頂得痛嘅！"},{"pid":"7bb58c14adcb4709224dc399b5b1c2b80c290ec6","tid":660431,"uid":6425,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T16:39:49.000Z","msg":"入到手術房，咁會叫你除衫，再幫你駁血壓計，心電圖果啲<br />\n麻醉科醫生會俾啲氧氣你聞，叫你MAK大眼深呼吸<br />\n之後係鹽水豆打藥俾你，你就會訓著嫁啦<br />\n醒番果刻已經做完手術<br />\n會有人大叫你個名，拍你，叫你深呼吸<br />\n到你有醒左有反應就會幫你抆條呼吸喉<br />\n之後就會推你出去復甦室觀察<br />\n<br />\n通常做完都會頭暈<br />\n眼訓: 正常，但如果眼訓到呼吸唔好，就會有好多人黎幫你手<br />\n嘔心/嘔: 太嚴重都有藥再打<br />\n痛: 都會有藥既<br />\n呼吸唔好: 會有條氧氣喉俾你，如果見你OK就機會唔洗用<br />\n<br />\n觀察半個鐘左右，OK既就會叫病房接你"},{"pid":"7f33207c1fd2baf394ff20507e5d4f274365d0ee","tid":660431,"uid":6425,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T16:44:13.000Z","msg":"我自己剝過四隻智慧齒，不過係局部麻醉做<br />\n我覺得做口既手術最煩係做完面腫，食唔到固體野<br />\n不過其實都唔係咩大手術，唔洗驚<br />\n做完手術一定痛，定時定侯食藥啦<br />\n應該好快好番"},{"pid":"aced49c7a49e126643591280579be85c850c94a2","tid":660431,"uid":14916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T16:48:34.000Z","msg":"我都係智慧齒搞到生咗個水瘤，全身麻醉拎咗出嚟，做完會痛一排食唔到嘢，當減下肥啦巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好快好返"},{"pid":"8776a678c754d953822dca4a316007ebcec8cd7e","tid":660431,"uid":147532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T17:10:57.000Z","msg":"唔驚嘅，吸一吸D麻醉氣體就冇哂知覺，醒返巳經係觀察房<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全身麻醉但唔係口腔手術"},{"pid":"4640dc291e4c75ab5bdd06c195f16271d8b85952","tid":660431,"uid":36334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T17:12:50.000Z","msg":"口水瘤，一入去打完麻醉，第二日就係張病床度，然後個晚發燒，麻醉完唔知點解好想飲可樂，明明唔想食野，剩係想飲可樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18fa47b3562abcd63f132d06423dbe329c4024b4","tid":660431,"uid":36121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T17:19:45.000Z","msg":"做過 剝晒四隻智慧齒<br />\n淨係記得做完後好眼瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff90010e8ea4c78ba8c81185b10df0b4d9a303d8","tid":660431,"uid":10241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aced49c7a49e126643591280579be85c850c94a2","tid":660431,"uid":14916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T16:48:34.000Z","msg":"我都係智慧齒搞到生咗個水瘤，全身麻醉拎咗出嚟，做完會痛一排食唔到嘢，當減下肥啦巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好快好返"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T17:20:11.000Z","msg":"我一次過抆晒4乾隻<br />\n痛左個幾兩個月,塊面腫到連行路瞓教都痛<br />\n果陣日日食雪糕同飲凍維他奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但瘦左成十幾磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab084c6bfa85e06400e116f966ae6c8ecd075adf","tid":660431,"uid":10464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff90010e8ea4c78ba8c81185b10df0b4d9a303d8","tid":660431,"uid":10241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aced49c7a49e126643591280579be85c850c94a2","tid":660431,"uid":14916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T16:48:34.000Z","msg":"我都係智慧齒搞到生咗個水瘤，全身麻醉拎咗出嚟，做完會痛一排食唔到嘢，當減下肥啦巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好快好返"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T17:20:11.000Z","msg":"我一次過抆晒4乾隻<br />\n痛左個幾兩個月,塊面腫到連行路瞓教都痛<br />\n果陣日日食雪糕同飲凍維他奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但瘦左成十幾磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T17:27:26.000Z","msg":"冇止痛藥畀咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前我做咗個放膿引流小手術<br />\n打左幾支麻醉都係好痛<br />\n好似話發炎 麻醉係冇乜用<br />\n嗰日做完喺醫院度喊咗三個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即刻食止痛藥都係痛到傻<br />\n護士個個過嚟關心我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會唔會有相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過之後嗰幾日食咗止痛藥就冇乜嘢<br />\n雖然都要一排消腫"},{"pid":"962dfde23dae8f1e766c0fa7a4dcf20f0cd013fa","tid":660431,"uid":88102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T17:53:44.000Z","msg":"醒返頭幾日成日流口水但自己唔知<br />\n又訓到醫院d枕頭全部血"},{"pid":"05148906238a9bcf4a23bc3eb14e3140de740e5b","tid":660431,"uid":50677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T17:56:05.000Z","msg":"幾年前係瑪麗醫院全身麻醉剝2隻智慧牙"},{"pid":"f9f75b76a11b766abfcc7af4fe06f4d5d3f35610","tid":660431,"uid":106375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T18:00:05.000Z","msg":"記得手術室會播歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"378e5079c0b12e770f841aa6f3c1817021cbd2b0","tid":660431,"uid":14916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff90010e8ea4c78ba8c81185b10df0b4d9a303d8","tid":660431,"uid":10241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aced49c7a49e126643591280579be85c850c94a2","tid":660431,"uid":14916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T16:48:34.000Z","msg":"我都係智慧齒搞到生咗個水瘤，全身麻醉拎咗出嚟，做完會痛一排食唔到嘢，當減下肥啦巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好快好返"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T17:20:11.000Z","msg":"我一次過抆晒4乾隻<br />\n痛左個幾兩個月,塊面腫到連行路瞓教都痛<br />\n果陣日日食雪糕同飲凍維他奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但瘦左成十幾磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T00:51:15.000Z","msg":"我都係四隻 但好快就想食通粉意粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea1754cc78634d4809a85e59525cd5e899f752a5","tid":660431,"uid":64009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T00:56:58.000Z","msg":"死左都係無感覺下死<br />\n怕咩"},{"pid":"0d62d8af9f9bd257dd9287e1859be13da0c13c3e","tid":660431,"uid":10241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"378e5079c0b12e770f841aa6f3c1817021cbd2b0","tid":660431,"uid":14916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff90010e8ea4c78ba8c81185b10df0b4d9a303d8","tid":660431,"uid":10241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aced49c7a49e126643591280579be85c850c94a2","tid":660431,"uid":14916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T16:48:34.000Z","msg":"我都係智慧齒搞到生咗個水瘤，全身麻醉拎咗出嚟，做完會痛一排食唔到嘢，當減下肥啦巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好快好返"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T17:20:11.000Z","msg":"我一次過抆晒4乾隻<br />\n痛左個幾兩個月,塊面腫到連行路瞓教都痛<br />\n果陣日日食雪糕同飲凍維他奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但瘦左成十幾磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T00:51:15.000Z","msg":"我都係四隻 但好快就想食通粉意粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T01:00:00.000Z","msg":"痛到仆街仲食到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我塊面變左正方形成個月先開始消腫<br />\n4隻都打橫生,仲有隻勁新神經線<br />\n全部要切牙肉先拎到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"679392a6cf9b4de61bee4896843c209cb1de2efb","tid":660431,"uid":14916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d62d8af9f9bd257dd9287e1859be13da0c13c3e","tid":660431,"uid":10241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"378e5079c0b12e770f841aa6f3c1817021cbd2b0","tid":660431,"uid":14916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff90010e8ea4c78ba8c81185b10df0b4d9a303d8","tid":660431,"uid":10241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T17:20:11.000Z","msg":"我一次過抆晒4乾隻<br />\n痛左個幾兩個月,塊面腫到連行路瞓教都痛<br />\n果陣日日食雪糕同飲凍維他奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但瘦左成十幾磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T00:51:15.000Z","msg":"我都係四隻 但好快就想食通粉意粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T01:00:00.000Z","msg":"痛到仆街仲食到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我塊面變左正方形成個月先開始消腫<br />\n4隻都打橫生,仲有隻勁新神經線<br />\n全部要切牙肉先拎到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T02:04:04.000Z","msg":"我好快就食得返嘢，佢話要用雪條棍練習我都冇練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係，仲要剝一隻大牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到而家食嘢，第一啖都會有啲痺"},{"pid":"19e393959e1fb9c535c3554e7eb888d2687ed22f","tid":660431,"uid":174013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T02:06:39.000Z","msg":"10歲做過<br />\n脫多生齒"},{"pid":"6a348392f5a3f341f96ea67acb47f06a8d1c3d38","tid":660431,"uid":15144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T12:40:46.000Z","msg":"切過扁桃腺<br />\n要禁食一日 入手術室前仲諗緊會唔會麻醉唔到，點知吸左一兩下就訓到死左<br />\n麻醉過左個傷口痛到痴線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋做手術個時啲血流左去氣管 搞到唔係幾抖到氣仲要食唔落野 醫院仲要比一碗好似白膠漿嘅野你食  又難吞又冇味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n番到屋企訓到半夜就嘔左舊乒乓球咁大嘅瘀血"},{"pid":"4875304f542fee51f6e649bf0c926846c7219045","tid":660431,"uid":171926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T13:42:26.000Z","msg":"全身麻醉就好似訓咗教咁，過程一d感覺都無，醒番哥時見到d護士收緊野準備走人。麻醉過咗傷口會有d痛，番屋企啪止痛藥就無乜事。<br />\n<br />\n利申：做過n次口腔手術"},{"pid":"7970b13dd2cccec148e80388eec2d620619ffd26","tid":660431,"uid":10464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4875304f542fee51f6e649bf0c926846c7219045","tid":660431,"uid":171926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T13:42:26.000Z","msg":"全身麻醉就好似訓咗教咁，過程一d感覺都無，醒番哥時見到d護士收緊野準備走人。麻醉過咗傷口會有d痛，番屋企啪止痛藥就無乜事。<br />\n<br />\n利申：做過n次口腔手術"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T15:40:05.000Z","msg":"點解咁慘要做n次嘅？"}]}